&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/TheLeadingHotelsoftheWorld.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-9217&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/TheLeadingHotelsoftheWorld.png&quot; alt=&quot;TheLeadingHotelsoftheWorld&quot; width=&quot;79&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Curious travelers see the world differently because they find inspiration in unexpected places. From former castles and palaces, to urban gems, mountain hideaways and private islands, our collection of more than 375 uncommon luxury hotels in 75 countries are united not by what makes them the same, but by the remarkable details that make them different.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brimming with antebellum homes and true southern charm, the city of Charleston captures a slice of American history. Located just steps from the Waterfront Park in the epicenter Historic District, the elegant 19th-century style Market Pavilion Hotel is built on land formerly below sea level and many of the artifacts on display, including Revolutionary War-era bottles and historic artwork, were uncovered on the seabed. They now adorn the guest rooms and public areas and are beautifully merged with contemporary works. The cascading rooftop pool, unique in the city and the Pavilion Bar draw a stylish crowd who admire the unobstructed view of the harbor and city skyline, while those with a taste for fine dining enjoy the award-winning Grill 225 Prime Steakhouse, just off the hotel lobby.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diners Club cardmembers must first visit&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lhw.com/online-offers/DCI?ppcode=DCI&amp;#038;pocode=1512NBR&amp;#038;ext=DNCLWEBLC16&amp;#038;utm_medium=link&amp;#038;utm_source=dnclweblc&amp;#038;utm_campaign=2016dnclweblc&amp;#038;utm_content=dncllcweb&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;this link&lt;/a&gt; &lt;strong&gt;to enroll in Leaders Club&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After enrolling in Leaders Club, cardmembers can take advantage of the following benefits when staying at a Leading Hotel:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Daily continental breakfast for two&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One-category room upgrade (subject to availability)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Earn one complimentary night at any Leading Hotel for every five qualifying stays completed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Early check-in, late check-out consideration (based on availability)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free internet access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unique welcome gift&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Making a Reservation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; In order to obtain all benefits available through membership in Leaders Club, Diners Club cardmembers must make hotel reservations through one of the booking channels listed below, and must also provide his or her Leaders Club membership number at the time of booking:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Through The Leading Hotels of the World &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lhw.com/property.aspx?pid=C6688E73-8317-4340-87AD-31E7AE28AAAC&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;website&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;(no other web-enabled booking engine qualifies for this eligibility requirement)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Through an&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://lhw.com/customer-care&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LHW Worldwide Reservations and Service Center&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Through the Loyalty Program, as provided on the back of the membership card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hotel reservations made directly with one of LHW&rsquo;s member hotels will not be eligible for the benefits of Leaders Club.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check the specific terms for canceling a reservation, as each hotel has a different policy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Membership in the Loyalty Program and Loyalty Program benefits are subject to the Leaders Club Terms &amp;#038; Conditions. LHW shall have the right to terminate the Loyalty Program or change the benefits at any time in its sole discretion, as provided therein.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Eligibility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; A Diners Club cardmember will be eligible to participate in the Offer provided he or she is not a Loyalty Program Member at the time he or she seeks to enroll in the Loyalty Program and has not been a Loyalty Program Member at any time during the immediately preceding twelve (12) month period.&nbsp;The Loyalty program membership will be valid for one (1) year only from the date of enrollment. After twelve (12) month from the effective date of the enrollment, the membership will expire and each Diners Club cardmember can then choose whether or not he or she wants to renew his or her membership at the then applicable membership fee.&lt;/p&gt;

